The Sarkin Kasuwar Magani in Kajuru local government area of Kaduna state, Malam Abdullah Haruna, popularly known as Dan Asabe, has been declared missing. Daily Trust gathered that he was missing since on Wednesday, December 26, 2018 after going to his farm to harvest potatoes. Details of his abduction remained sketchy but a youth leader in Kasuwar Magani who preferred anonymity said no news of him since he went missing. “He went to his farm at Dutsen Gaya community closed to Kasuwar Magani on Wednesday and since then we have not heard from him. No demand was made. Some security agents went to the bush searching for him but he was not found,” he said. The spokesman of Kaduna state police command, DSP Yakubu Sabo, couldn’t be reach for official comments as his line wasn’t reachable as at the time of filing this report.  Details later…